<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer15011301244211961899">Set in the Northern Ireland of the 1980’s, <i>Cal</i> tells the story of a young Catholic man living in a Protestant area. For Cal, some choices are devastatingly simple: he can work in an abattoir that nauseates him or join the dole queue; he can brood on his past or plan a future with Marcella. <br/><br/> Springing out of the fear and violence of Ulster, <i>Cal </i>is a haunting love story that</span>
  <span id="freeText15011301244211961899" style="display:none">Set in the Northern Ireland of the 1980’s, <i>Cal</i> tells the story of a young Catholic man living in a Protestant area. For Cal, some choices are devastatingly simple: he can work in an abattoir that nauseates him or join the dole queue; he can brood on his past or plan a future with Marcella. <br /><br /> Springing out of the fear and violence of Ulster, <i>Cal </i>is a haunting love story that unfolds in a land where tenderness and innocence can only flicker briefly in the dark.</span>
