<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">A tiny spoiler, but:<br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>Yes. She&apos;s the widow of the man he helped murder.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">A tiny spoiler, but:<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Yes. She's the widow of the man he helped murder.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
